Products.Name: Magnum Tub Ice Cream Classic
Products.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Magnum Tub Ice Cream Classic' has a supply limit of 36. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Products.SmallFormatDescription: Magnum Tub Ice Cream Classic
Products.FullDescription: Magnum Tub Ice Cream Classic
Products.RichDescription:
MAGNUM ICE CREAM CLASSIC 440 ML

Experience Magnum Classic in a tub. Made to be broken. Discover the ultimate Magnum cracking chocolate and velvety ice cream experience with the new Magnum Classic tub. Squeeze the pack and crack the thick Magnum chocolate shell that envelops the delicious velvety vanilla flavoured ice cream. There you will find cracking Magnum chocolate shards throughout the tub, so you can have a rich and intense chocolate experience in every spoonful. Magnum tub makes your nights-in even more pleasurable. Discover the full Magnum ice cream tub range with Magnum Almond and Magnum White flavours. Our philosophy: Since 1989, Pleasure Seekers around the world have been discovering Magnum. Thick Chocolate. Velvety ice cream. The perfect balance. Magnum never stopped working, adding new flavours. New textures. We love film, we love fashion. We believe a day without pleasure is a day lost. So make time to indulge in a little glamour. Magnum chocolate dessert ice cream is made from our highest quality cocoa beans, sustainably grown and carefully selected by Rainforest Alliance Certified™ farmers. Magnum cocoa beans have a long way to go before they become Magnum chocolate. We’re working closely with the Rainforest Alliance to make sure all our cocoa beans are responsibly sourced to produce our icecreams, sticks and tubs, in every flavour, with the best chocolate quality. It’s about quality and sustainability throughout every step of the journey. Every Magnum stick, every Magnum tub represent the perfect, indulgent and delicious treat or snack for any family. Since 1989, Pleasure Seekers around the world have been discovering Magnum, and we have been taking pleasure very seriously. Thick Chocolate. Smooth ice cream. The perfect balance. To us, pleasure is everything. The pleasure of each individual and their freedom to experience it genuinely and in full. We know pleasure can be found in both the smallest and the biggest things. But only if you are brave enough will you really find your pleasure, your true pleasure that stays with you. We are Magnum, the champions of true pleasure.

New Magnum Ice cream Tub. Classic chocolate and velvety vanilla flavoured ice cream in a perfect icecream confection pint.

New. Experience Magnum icecream in a tub to make your nights-in even more pleasurable

Vanilla flavoured Ice cream and Chocolate shards in a cracking chocolate shell

Magnum chocolate dessert ice cream is certified by Rainforest Alliance in any flavour.

Magnum chocolate dessert ice cream is certified by Rainforest Alliance in any flavour. Magnum sticks are a delicious treat for every family.

Magnum chocolate dessert icecream is made from our highest quality cocoa beans, sustainably grown and carefully selected to deliver the best chocolate flavours to you.

Products.FullDescription: Super Nature Super Foods Mediterranean Polenta
Products.RichDescription:
Welcome to a revolution in healthy eating.

The Super Nature range is bursting with some of the healthiest, most natural ingredients around. 

We're talking superfoods, loaded with nutrients to energise your body, fuel your brain, fight infection and help you stay lean for longer. 

Our chefs have crafted this unique range of super tasty snap frozen meals specially for busy people like you. 

Each meal is carefully prepared to combine these healthy ingredients to create super tasty meals. 

Now, you no longer have to choose between health and taste - Super Nature is packed with both. 

Enjoy! 

Polenta.

Polenta's slow-release carbohydrates keep you energised for longer. It's also a great source of vitamin A and zinc to give your skin a healthy glow. 

Broccoli.

Feeling strung out? Then broccoli could be just the thing. High levels of vitamin K, C and A help soothe stressed bodies and aid detoxification. 

Cannellini beans.

These tasty little beans are low in fat, high in fibre and brimming with magnesium, iron and folate. Like all complex carbs, they're also a great source of energy. 

Sun dried tomatoes.

Sun dried tomatoes are sky-high in a bright red carotene pigment called lycopene, a powerful antioxidant that helps fight free radicals. 

Spinach.

Low in calories yet brimming in vitamins and iron, spinach is a super source of antioxidants like flavonoids and vitamins C and A. 

Find out more about our amazing superfood ingredients at www.supernaturefoods.com.au

Slow cooked polenta topped with a Mediterranean style sauce of sun dried tomatoes, mushrooms, black olives and cannellini beans. Served with broccoli, red capsicum, spinach and topped with a sprinkle of cheese.
